   Accueil LEARN MORE Accueil OUR RANKINGS IN STUDENT
   SATISFACTION When Maclean’s conducted its survey of student
   satisfaction for its 2019 university rankings for primarily
   undergraduate universities, Bishop’s students once again stood out as
   the most satisfied in Canada. That was also the case for the 2018
   edition, the 2017 edition and the 2016 edition of the rankings. #1
   Accueil BE CURIOUS. BE PURPLE.
   BU. Challenging courses and passionate professors are at the heart of
   the BU educational experience. Through them, we offer outstanding
   opportunities for students to learn – and live – what they love. Our
   ultimate goal is to help our students advance, explore and grow.
   ACADEMIC PROGRAMS
